(597,	3,	'iPhone 5 Diagnostic Service',	'&lt;p&gt;iPhone 5 diagnostics are the sure way to see what is going on with your device. From battery to software tests, we can see exactly what your iPhone 5 needs to run at full speed ahead! Once our free iPhone 5 diagnostic is performed, one of our knowledgeable technicians will speak with you regarding what the repair process will entail, and what the repair cost will be. So if your iPhone 5 is acting up in any way, come in for free diagnostics, and put your iPhone on the road to recovery.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Diagnostic Service? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Diagnostic Service!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Diagnostic Service, iPhone 5, Diagnostic Service'),
(603,	1,	'HTC Incredible Glass/Touch Screen &amp; LCD Replacement',	'Glass is not always the only thing to break on a HTC Incredible. After a drop the LCD can suffer damage as well, leading to a black screen, lines across the display or a screen that does not respond properly to touch or swipe gestures. Stop in today, and we can get your HTC Incredible started on its very own glass/LCD repair process.',	'Are you in need of a HTC Incredible Glass/Touch Screen &amp; LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your HTC Incredible Glass/Touch Screen &amp; LCD Replacement!',	'',	'HTC Incredible Glass/Touch Screen &amp; LCD Replacement, HTC Incredible, Glass &amp; LCD Replacement'),
(598,	1,	'iPhone 5 Water Damage Repair Diagnostic',	'An iPhone 5 that went swimming used to be sadly reduced to spending the rest of its life as a paperweight. But not anymore! Let the repair professionals at uBreakiFix complete our extensive liquid damage diagnostic process on your device! The process will include checking to see which components still work, which need replacing and what your iPhone 5 needs to get back up and running in as little time as possible. Once the trained staff at uBreakiFix pinpoints the repair and components needed, they will contact you with a repair quote and time frame for completion. If on the off chance your device is not repairable, it will not cost you anything, the technicians will provide you with a quote before completing the repair! Stop by a local uBreakiFix location today and let the professionals save your iPhone 5 from a life as a paperweight!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5 Water Damage Repair Diagnostic? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5 Water Damage Repair Diagnostic!',	'',	'iPhone 5 Water Damage Repair Diagnostic, iPhone 5, Water Damage Repair Diagnostic'),
(587,	1,	'Amazon Kindle Fire HD Diagnostic',	'Amazon Kindle Fires can start displaying symptoms of strange behavior at any point, for a variety of reasons. If you have noticed a change in your Amazon Kindle Fire\'s functionality- from charging, screen issues, or speaker problems, let the trained professionals at uBreakiFix run a free diagnostic service on your Amazon Kindle Fire. The trained technicians at uBreakiFix will perform tests on your Amazon Kindle Fire to see what exactly is going on, and what we can do to get your device healthy and operating at full capacity again!',	'Are you in need of a Amazon Kindle Fire HD Diagnostic? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Amazon Kindle Fire HD Diagnostic!',	'',	'Amazon Kindle Fire HD Diagnostic, Amazon Kindle Fire, Diagnostic Service'),
(588,	1,	'Google Nexus 7 Diagnostic',	'Google Nexus 7s can start displaying symptoms of strange behavior at any point, for a variety of reasons. If you have noticed a change in your Google Nexus 7\'s functionality- from charging, screen issues, or speaker problems, let the trained professionals at uBreakiFix run a free diagnostic service on your Google Nexus 7. The trained technicians at uBreakiFix will perform tests on your Google Nexus 7 to see what exactly is going on, and what we can do to get your device healthy and operating at full capacity again!',	'Are you in need of a Google Nexus 7 Diagnostic? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Google Nexus 7 Diagnostic!',	'',	'Google Nexus 7 Diagnostic, Google Nexus 7, Diagnostic Service'),
(589,	1,	'Google Nexus 10 Diagnostic (Coming Soon)',	'Google Nexus 10s can start displaying symptoms of strange behavior at any point, for a variety of reasons. If you have noticed a change in your Google Nexus 10\'s functionality- from charging, screen issues, or speaker problems, let the trained professionals at uBreakiFix run a free diagnostic service on your Google Nexus 10. The trained technicians at uBreakiFix will perform tests on your Google Nexus 10 to see what exactly is going on, and what we can do to get your device healthy and operating at full capacity again!',	'Are you in need of a Google Nexus 10 Diagnostic (Coming Soon)? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Google Nexus 10 Diagnostic (Coming Soon)!',	'',	'Google Nexus 10 Diagnostic (Coming Soon), Google Nexus 10, Diagnostic Service'),
(590,	1,	'Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Diagnostic',	'Is your Samsung Galaxy Note 10 acting sparatically? Not charging, LCD flicker, software bugs, not connecting to wi-fi? If your Samsung Galaxy Note 10 has an issue, stop by today for a free diagnostic service! A uBreakiFix highly trained technician will run a variety of tests on your Samsung Galaxy Note 10, figure out what is malfunctioning and provide you with a repair quote and time estimate. Samsung Galaxy Note 10 diagnostic services are always free and if the device is unrepairable for any reason, you don\'t pay anything!',	'Are you in need of a Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Diagnostic? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Diagnostic!',	'',	'Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Diagnostic, Samsung Galaxy Note 10, Diagnostic Service'),
(591,	1,	'Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Glass/Touch Screen Replacement',	'Samsung Galaxy Note 10 that have suffered damage to the glass are a pain in the neck! Don\'t try to see through the shatters any longer- stop by today for our Samsung Galaxy Note 10 glass replacement service.',	'Are you in need of a Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Glass/Touch Screen Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Glass/Touch Screen Replacement!',	'',	'Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Glass/Touch Screen Replacement, Samsung Galaxy Note 10, Glass Replacement'),
