(67,	2,	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement',	'One of our most popular repairs, if you have an At&amp;t iPhone 4 with a glass/LCD that is cracked, has a distorted image, no image, or otherwise malfunctioning, stop by uBreakiFix. Join our many happy customers who no longer try to work around a cracked screen on their At&amp;t iPhone 4!',	'Are you in need of a At&amp;t iPhone 4 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement!',	'',	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement, At&amp;t iPhone 4, Glass &amp; LCD Replacement'),
