(688,	3,	'iPhone 5S Glass &amp; LCD Replacement',	'&lt;p&gt;One of our most popular repairs, if you have an iPhone 5S with a glass/LCD that is cracked, has a distorted image, no image, or otherwise malfunctioning, stop by uBreakiFix. Join our many happy customers who no longer try to work around a cracked screen on their iPhone 5S!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 5S Glass &amp; LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 5S Glass &amp; LCD Replacement!',	'',	'iPhone 5S Glass &amp; LCD Replacement, iPhone 5S, Glass &amp; LCD Replacement'),
