(962,	3,	'Samsung Galaxy S5 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement',	'&lt;p&gt;Your Samsung Galaxy S5 glass cracked, and now your LCD is broken too- what to do? Stop by today for our Samsung Galaxy S5 glass/LCD replacement service, so you can have a working screen again!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n',	'Are you in need of a Samsung Galaxy S5 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your Samsung Galaxy S5 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement!',	'',	'Samsung Galaxy S5 Glass &amp; LCD Replacement, Samsung Galaxy S5, Glass &amp; LCD Replacement'),
