(881,	2,	'Diagnostic pour HTC EVO 4G LTE',	'Votre #téléphoneintelligent agit-il étrangement? L\'écran ne fonctionne pas bien? Vous avez des problèmes de son ou de navigation? Peut-être que ça ne va tout simplement pas? Notre service de diagnostic pour #téléphoneintelligent peut trouver ce qui cloche et rétablir le bon fonctionnement de votre #téléphoneintelligent!',	'Besoin d\'une HTC EVO 4G LTE Diagnostic? Notre personnel professionnel et courtois peut effectuer la HTC EVO 4G LTE Diagnostic dont vous avez besoin!',	'0',	'Diagnostic pour HTC EVO 4G LTE'),
(77,	3,	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Battery Replacement',	'Is your At&amp;t iPhone 4 battery sleeping on the job? Not charging, not holding a charge, or dying faster than it should? Our At&amp;t iPhone 4 battery replacement service is just the thing you need! Stop in today, to see how we can get your battery back on the job!',	'Are you in need of a At&amp;t iPhone 4 Battery Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 Battery Replacement!',	'',	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Battery Replacement, At&amp;t iPhone 4, Battery Replacement'),
(76,	3,	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Cover Replacement',	'Is the back of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 in rough shape? Cracked, scratched, or just plain embarrasing? You don\'t have to try and hide the back of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 any longer! Visit uBreakiFix today so you can make your At&amp;t iPhone 4 brand new again, with the help of a new back cover.',	'Are you in need of a At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Cover Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Cover Replacement!',	'',	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Cover Replacement, At&amp;t iPhone 4, Back Cover Replacement'),
(75,	3,	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Camera Replacement',	'Having trouble taking pictures on your At&amp;t iPhone 4? Is the camera cracked, not opening, or otherwise obscured? We can help you! Bring your iPhone in, and we will let you know exactly what your camera needs, or replace it, so you can get back to taking pictures in the blink of an eye!',	'Are you in need of a At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Camera Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Camera Replacement!',	'',	'At&amp;t iPhone 4 Back Camera Replacement, At&amp;t iPhone 4, Camera Replacement'),
(74,	3,	'iPhone 4S White Back Cover Replacement',	'Whether your iPhone 4S\'s white back cover is damaged, or you would just like to switch things up, this is the repair service for you. Stop by today for a white iPhone 4S back cover replacement, and be proud of your phone again!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 4S White Back Cover Replacement? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 4S White Back Cover Replacement!',	'',	'iPhone 4S White Back Cover Replacement, iPhone 4S, White Back Cover Replacement'),
(73,	3,	'iPhone 4S Front Camera Repair',	'Having problems taking a selfie with your front-facing iPhone 4S camera? Bring in your iPhone 4S today for for front camera repair, so you can get back to taking selfies with confidence!',	'Are you in need of a iPhone 4S Front Camera Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your iPhone 4S Front Camera Repair!',	'',	'iPhone 4S Front Camera Repair, iPhone 4S, Front Camera Repair'),
