(648,	3,	'XBOX 360 Slim Red Ring of Death Repair',	'The Red Ring of Death is something every XBOX 360 user has heard of- and dreads. If this notorious light has made its way on to your XBOX, then stop by today for our XBOX 360 Red Ring of Death Repair service. Our technicians will make sure this light haunts you no longer, and you can get back to regular XBOX use in no time!',	'Are you in need of a XBOX 360 Slim Red Ring of Death Repair? Allow our professional and friendly staff take care of your XBOX 360 Slim Red Ring of Death Repair!',	'',	'XBOX 360 Slim Red Ring of Death Repair, XBOX 360 Slim, Red Ring of Death Repair'),
